      "title": "Cherry-picks by Downstream Branch",
      "description": "Total cherry-pick commits per downstream rhoai-x.y branch. Each cherry-pick to a frozen release branch means a production-blocking issue required an out-of-band fix. Branches with the most cherry-picks had the most turbulent post-release periods.",
